data.description: Welcome home to 12102 Branding Iron Court! This beautiful Wellington home is ideally situated on a private cul-de-sac. Located in the desireable Pinewood neighbordood, a stones throw to A-rated schools, shopping, parks, restaurants and equestrian activities. Located on nearly 1-acre of land, fully fenced, the beautiful park-like yard is adjorned with beautiful mature palms, crepe myrtles and has irrigation throughout. Inside the home you will find updated tile flooring throughout, stainless steel appliances, granite counter tops, new light fixtures, a dual-sided fireplace and a remodeled master bedroom/bathroom. The master has it's own private patio space that leads to the beautiful backyard. Newer roof and A/C unit. There is ample room for the pool of your dreams and or a guesthouse.
